  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      MRI &amp; MRE in infants
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the present pilot study is to determine the feasibility of using MRI and MRE
      to evaluate the liver in infants with suspected liver disease.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
