  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Infants &lt; 6 months of age

          -  Known liver disease based (liver enzymes, bilirubin, and/or GGT at least twice the
             upper limit of normal for age)

          -  Parental/LAR permission obtained

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Standard MRI exclusion criteria as set forth by the CCHMC Division of Radiology

          -  Severe coagulopathy (INR &gt; 3 or platelets &lt;50,000)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
